{"word":"G4917 - συνθλάω - synthláō - soon-thlah'-o - Break","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνθλάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synthláō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-thlah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Break</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நொறுங்கிப்போ"},{"paragraph":"to break to pieces, shatter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <b>&#x03B8;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> t<b>hlao&#x0304;</b> (to <i>crush</i>); to <i>dash together</i>, that is, <i>shatter:</i> - break.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}